This paper deals with automatic image description systems, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of crowd workers, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
